      <title>卖空者安德鲁·莱夫特被指控犯有证券欺诈罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/short-seller-andrew-left-is-charged-with-securities-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当局称，著名卖空者安德鲁·莱夫特试图快速轻松地赚钱并实施欺诈。他被指控利用其公司 Citron 从涉及近二十家公司的非法交易中获取约 2000 万美元的利润。彭博社的 Bailey Lipshultz 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/short-seller-andrew-left-is-charged-with-securities-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 14:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据支持 9 月降息，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/treasuries-rally-as-data-backs-the-case-for-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储最青睐的通胀指标巩固了交易员对九月份降息的预期，美国国债价格在动荡的一周结束时上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/treasuries-rally-as-data-backs-the-case-for-a-september-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
